{"tid":2223613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家又想spin開話題，令大家唔記得聽日係咩日子","createTime":"2020-09-30T03:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:42:07.000Z","uid":309558,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0aeb9f1d29f3586d692c1cc4115ebd406d8c5843","tid":2223613,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:21:56.000Z","msg":"冇錯就係一班中共委任議員連聽日有遊行都唔夠膽提，我哋唔可以俾對家咁樣操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日要靠香港人自己企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGuQ0Jb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGuQ0Jb.jpg&h=d75bfce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOgDp9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOgDp9S.jpg&h=62327146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjyuwPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjyuwPU.jpg&h=a32776c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【#十一大遊行 光復香港 時代革命】<br />\n三台同步<br />\n<br />\n日期｜10.1 中秋節<br />\n時間｜2PM 起步<br />\n路線｜東角道 至 菲林明道<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://t.me/chosumhangdong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fchosumhangdong&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=9adc3ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/chosumhangdong</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiAnthemLawChannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiAnthemLawChannel&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=83b42395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiAnthemLawChannel</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ihavealight\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fihavealight&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=0f4a8dbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iha